welcome_message_body: Welcome to Seattle! Get ready to experience the charm of the Emerald City, known for its stunning waterfront, iconic Space Needle, and vibrant music scene. Take some time to explore and enjoy all that Seattle has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options, retail stores, and rental car services.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for private and charter flights, with a separate entrance and security checkpoint.
